{"tid":549883,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇《9號秘事》 Inside No.9?","createTime":"2018-02-04T06:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T02:52:11.000Z","uid":67702,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb748f9d0dbf90d5817fd974129d39a30d855d8","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/135722_1f7e0542648a1c931560c3429da2e83b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F135722_1f7e0542648a1c931560c3429da2e83b.jpg&h=112e5944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同屬英劇，好多人會將Inside No.9 同Black Mirror 比較<br />\n但我覺得Black Mirror係帶有驚悚元素嘅科幻片，Sci-fi 感較強<br />\n後者其實係帶有恐怖元素嘅懸疑片，犯罪、懸疑、恐怖、復仇集於一身<br />\n鍾意睇twist嘅人，真係行過路過唔好錯過，一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先介紹下兩位編劇 ： <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/143252_0a31afa0730a9e66dff4fb97d93b8d52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F143252_0a31afa0730a9e66dff4fb97d93b8d52.jpg&h=a142f394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSteve Pemberton（左）同Reece Shearsmith（右）<br />\n呢兩條友簡直係痴線嘅<br />\n作啲故仔曲折離奇，又帶點on9，有幽默又有親情<br />\n仲要係佢地兩個自己演埋出黎<br />\nCrazy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9號秘事每一集都係獨立故仔<br />\n每一集都係得30 分鐘<br />\n小弟呢排日日番工坐車就會開黎睇，好頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由2014年首播，到今年為止已經出到第四季喇<br />\n<br />\n好，事不宜遲，等我簡單講下第一季先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/143521_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F143521_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg&h=353235f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS1E1 Sardines <br />\n喺婚宴上，大家玩沙丁魚遊戲<br />\n特別版捉依因，捉到人就要同對方企埋一齊<br />\n唔到最後都唔知邊個係奸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/143640_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F143640_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=b26ba701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS1E2 A Quiet Night In <br />\n兩個笨賊去富豪屋企偷野<br />\n呢集幾似默劇，對白唔多<br />\n兩個賊on9得黎幾搞笑<br />\n帶點Mr bean 的影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/143827_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F143827_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=4c9446c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS1E3 Tom ＆ Gerri <br />\n乞衣闖入你屋企最後搶走埋你嘅生活<br />\n呢集仲有Gemma Arterton 客串，我覺得佢好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後個twist 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/144348_0ff23d351755ef19a15eae8aca417b55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F144348_0ff23d351755ef19a15eae8aca417b55.png&h=44e9d06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS1E4 Last Gasp<br />\n有個明星去咗一個有有病嘅妹妹屋企幫佢過生日，<br />\n佢吹吹下氣球死鬼咗<br />\n探討人性嘅貪婪、黑暗<br />\n最後妹妹做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c8991d404d91ddb21e28b2a04179b193762d1e","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"S2E2 係我睇過最好睇嘅電視，S4E2緊隨其後<br />\n<br />\n兩位編劇舊作Psychoville都正，一開始會睇Inside No.9 都係因為知係佢地作品，嗰時根本冇留意係咩嚟，結果睇Sardines好驚喜"},{"pid":"08fd813b7a2fc7c63bd11084408dd167e59d7948","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c8991d404d91ddb21e28b2a04179b193762d1e","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"S2E2 係我睇過最好睇嘅電視，S4E2緊隨其後<br />\n<br />\n兩位編劇舊作Psychoville都正，一開始會睇Inside No.9 都係因為知係佢地作品，嗰時根本冇留意係咩嚟，結果睇Sardines好驚喜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"S4E2 真係好正<br />\n成套劇好似唱緊歌咁<br />\n對白好流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e851c6ede1526369d69ac72221987bb51d2f9d","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08fd813b7a2fc7c63bd11084408dd167e59d7948","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c8991d404d91ddb21e28b2a04179b193762d1e","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"S2E2 係我睇過最好睇嘅電視，S4E2緊隨其後<br />\n<br />\n兩位編劇舊作Psychoville都正，一開始會睇Inside No.9 都係因為知係佢地作品，嗰時根本冇留意係咩嚟，結果睇Sardines好驚喜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"S4E2 真係好正<br />\n成套劇好似唱緊歌咁<br />\n對白好流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"佢地啲對白成日好似流水咁，我會追唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今季又得返一集，好似仲未有消息話有新一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07df7ceb0462b33aa50cdf1aa913a4474cec430","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"btw巴打漏咗第五六集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759bd2522f70c9dcb6af1e53db7a7aa7340bf80d","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07df7ceb0462b33aa50cdf1aa913a4474cec430","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"btw巴打漏咗第五六集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"未得閒寫呀<br />\n同埋連登冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753bb661032bd283bf6fdebad6e7d505280eedec","tid":549883,"uid":43217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n利申 追曬1 2 季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3e9165d864aed349a3212b59607fba58182a80","tid":549883,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"我好驚睇恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正想睇懸疑口味但又唔驚嚇<br />\n呢隻好啱我口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34b427f94b1950a5ee8dd450d64a12bf36a424c","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753bb661032bd283bf6fdebad6e7d505280eedec","tid":549883,"uid":43217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n利申 追曬1 2 季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"第四季都好精采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36bb2f62d2db6cbfb30ea5c3f36fd5185755810","tid":549883,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3e9165d864aed349a3212b59607fba58182a80","tid":549883,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"我好驚睇恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正想睇懸疑口味但又唔驚嚇<br />\n呢隻好啱我口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n佢啲twist 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc64d0ad4c3c58f71858c0c33d85d1e35105c28","tid":549883,"uid":78485,"like":0,"dis